{"title": "Sermons of a Buddhist Abbot", "description": "Look! it's the science of sitting, No! it's the science of meditating, No! it's Zen. If you wanted to know anything regarding Zen Buddhism and you did not have the opportunity then here is your chance to listen to the wisdom of a Zen Buddhist Abbot who toured the United States in 1905-6 and most of the sections in this book were lectures that were given to the American Audience, which is why this work is nicknamed as \"Zen for Americans.\"<br /><br />\"The Zen that can be explained is not the Zen\" said the second patriarch to Bodhi Dharma but this book tries to explain the basic principles that can help you get started on the journey of experiencing Zen. Some of the essays in this book were used as a reference by Leo Tolstoy in one of his works. (Summary by sidhu177)", "duration": 18718, "language": "English", "authors": [{"id": "10100", "name": "Soyen Shaku"}], "coverArt": "http://archive.org/download/LibrivoxCdCoverArt33/sermonsbuddhist_1310.jpg", "copyright_year": "1906", "genres": ["Other religions"], "supporters": [{"role": "Read by", "name": "LibriVox Volunteers"}, {"role": "Book Coordinator", "name": "sid"}, {"role": "Meta Coordinator", "name": "Laurie Anne Walden"}, {"role": "Proof Listener", "name": "Lucretia B."}], "sections": [{"section": 0, "title": "Translator's Preface", "readers": [7255], "path": "http://www.archive.org/download/sermons_buddhistabbot_1310_librivox/soba_00_shaku_64kb.mp3", "duration": 313}, {"section": 1, "title": "The Sutra of Forty-two Chapters", "readers": [7255], "path": "http://www.archive.org/download/sermons_buddhistabbot_1310_librivox/soba_01_shaku_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1253}, {"section": 2, "title": "The God-Conception of Buddhism", "readers": [6670], "path": "http://www.archive.org/download/sermons_buddhistabbot_1310_librivox/soba_02_shaku_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1275}, {"section": 3, "title": "Assertions and Denials", "readers": [8388], "path": "http://www.archive.org